<DOCNO> LA012994-0087 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 008190 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
January 29, 1994, Saturday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 10; Column 1; Foreign Desk 
</P>
