Colleen Hudson's 700th game at Fullerton. Riley, the winningest women's 
basketball coach in California community college history, has a mark of 557-143 
at Fullerton. She is retiring as a coach at the end of the season. 
</P>
<P>
 Cypress 82, Rancho Santiago 31 -- Sara Works had 28 points, and Yolanda 
Hearvey added 19 for host Cypress (19-7, 4-3). Rancho Santiago is 3-15, 0-7. 
</P>
