 Highland 63, Littlerock 55 -- Golden League scoring leaders Jonathan George of 
Littlerock and Pharoah Davis of Highland each had 24 points and 10 rebounds, 
but sophomore John Burrell made the difference for host Highland (13-6, 8-3). 
