<P>
EARTHQUAKE: THE LONG ROAD BACK; A POST-QUAKE SHOPPING GUIDE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Some San Fernando Valley shopping malls sustained major damage during the 
recent earthquake, most notably the Northridge Fashion Center. But many stores 
in the Valley area remain entirely or partially open. Here's an update on 
shopping malls in the Valley region: Antelope Valley Mall 
</P>
