<DOCNO> LA012994-0240 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 008343 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
January 29, 1994, Saturday, Valley Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 22; Column 1; Metro Desk 
